sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Client
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>Bearer Token Auth
    participant API as DS Pipelines API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow Controller<br/>8001/TCP HTTP
    participant Workflow as Workflow Pod<br/>Pipeline Execution
    participant Minio as Minio S3<br/>9000/TCP HTTP<br/>S3 Signature
    participant MLMD as ML Metadata gRPC<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL Auth
    participant Envoy as MLMD Envoy Proxy<br/>9090/TCP gRPC

    %% Flow 1: Pipeline Submission
    Note over User,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission via API
    User->>Route: POST /apis/v1/pipelines<br/>HTTPS, Bearer Token (OAuth)
    Route->>OAuth: Forward request<br/>TLS 1.3
    OAuth->>OAuth: Validate OAuth token
    OAuth->>API: Forward to API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    API->>DB: Store pipeline metadata<br/>3306/TCP, MySQL Auth
    DB-->>API: Confirmation
    API->>Minio: Upload pipeline YAML<br/>9000/TCP HTTP, S3 Signature
    Minio-->>API: Artifact stored
    API-->>OAuth: Pipeline created (JSON)
    OAuth-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: Pipeline ID

    %% Flow 2: Pipeline Execution
    Note over User,DB: Flow 2: Pipeline Execution (Scheduled or Manual)
    User->>Route: POST /apis/v1/runs<br/>HTTPS, Bearer Token
    Route->>OAuth: Forward request
    OAuth->>API: Create run<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    API->>DB: Store run metadata<br/>3306/TCP
    DB-->>API: Run ID
    API->>Argo: Submit workflow<br/>8001/TCP HTTP, SA Token
    Argo-->>API: Workflow accepted
    API-->>OAuth: Run created
    OAuth-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: Run ID

    %% Flow 3: Workflow Execution
    Note over Argo,MLMD: Flow 3: Workflow Pod Execution
    Argo->>Workflow: Create workflow pod<br/>Kubernetes API
    Workflow->>Minio: Download input artifacts<br/>9000/TCP HTTP, S3 Signature
    Minio-->>Workflow: Artifacts
    Workflow->>Workflow: Execute pipeline step
    Workflow->>MLMD: Track artifact metadata<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    MLMD->>DB: Store metadata<br/>3306/TCP
    DB-->>MLMD: Confirmation
    MLMD-->>Workflow: Metadata recorded
    Workflow->>Minio: Upload output artifacts<br/>9000/TCP HTTP
    Minio-->>Workflow: Upload complete
    Workflow-->>Argo: Step complete

    %% Flow 4: State Persistence
    Note over Argo,DB: Flow 4: Persistence Agent Sync
    Argo->>Argo: Workflow state change
    activate Argo
    Argo-->>API: Workflow event
    API->>DB: Update run status<br/>3306/TCP, MySQL Auth
    DB-->>API: Confirmed
    deactivate Argo

    %% Flow 5: Artifact Retrieval via UI
    Note over User,Envoy: Flow 5: Artifact Retrieval via UI
    User->>Route: GET /<br/>HTTPS, Bearer Token
    Route->>OAuth: UI request
    OAuth->>UI: Forward to UI Pod<br/>8443/TCP
    UI->>API: GET /apis/v1/runs/{id}<br/>8888/TCP HTTP, Bearer Token
    API->>DB: Query run metadata<br/>3306/TCP
    DB-->>API: Run details
    API-->>UI: Run metadata (JSON)
    UI->>Envoy: GET artifacts lineage<br/>9090/TCP gRPC
    Envoy->>MLMD: Query metadata<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    MLMD->>DB: Get artifact metadata<br/>3306/TCP
    DB-->>MLMD: Metadata
    MLMD-->>Envoy: gRPC response
    Envoy-->>UI: Lineage data
    UI->>Minio: Download artifact<br/>80/TCP HTTP, S3 Signature
    Minio-->>UI: Artifact content
    UI-->>OAuth: Rendered UI
    OAuth-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: UI with artifacts
